Description:
    Generates a form-object for the given resource operation with tests.

    Example:
      `rails generate active_model:form_object user update`

      For RSpec it creates:
      Form-object:  app/form_objects/user_update.rb
      Test:         spec/form_objects/user_update_spec.rb

      For MiniTest it creates:
      Form-object:  app/form_objects/user_update.rb
      Test:         test/form_objects/user_update_test.rb

      For TestUnit it creates:
      Form-object:  app/form_objects/user_update.rb
      Test:         test/unit/form_objects/user_update_test.rb
